data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Lake Nona, where luxury and tranquility converge. Nestled on a peaceful street, 12777 Hershko Aly boasts an exquisite residence that combines modern elegance with timeless design. This meticulously crafted property offers a lifestyle of comfort and sophistication.  Prime Location: Located in the prestigious Lake Nona community, this property provides convenient access to top-rated schools, medical facilities, shopping, dining, and recreational amenities.  Architectural Masterpiece: The home's architecture seamlessly blends contemporary elements with classic charm. From the moment you enter, you'll be captivated by the thoughtful design and attention to detail.  Spacious Interiors: The residence features an open floor plan, creating a sense of spaciousness and connectivity. The living spaces are bathed in natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and entertaining.  Gourmet Kitchen: The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with high-end appliances, custom cabinetry, and a stylish center island. It's the perfect setting for culinary enthusiasts and social gatherings.  Luxurious Bedrooms: The master suite is a private retreat, offering a sanctuary of comfort and style. Additional bedrooms are generously sized, providing ample space for family members or guests.  Garage and Parking: A spacious garage provides secure parking for your vehicles, and the driveway offers additional parking space for guests.    Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional property in Lake Nona. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and experience the epitome of luxury living in Orlando.
